If format function of the serial port is called it will disable the serial port.

For example this will not print anything:

``` c++
#include "mbed.h"

Serial pc(USBTX, USBRX);

int main()
{
    pc.baud(115200);
    pc.format(8, SerialBase::None, 1);
    pc.printf("Program started\r\n");

    for(;;){}
}
```

